sentences.english: Prices are differents depend on the type.
sentences.chinese: 价格根据型号有所不同。
丹若有所思地摩挲着下巴。

sentences.english: Listen to the tape and find out the main idea of this article and how it is organized.
sentences.chinese: 通过听录音磁带，来帮助学生对文章的结构有所了解。

sentences.english: The other thing to realize is that all writers think they suck.
sentences.chinese: 另外一个要认识的事情是所有作家认为他们有所得。

sentences.english: We should be prepared for any contingency.
sentences.chinese: 我们应该对任何应急情况有所准备。

sentences.english: As of Tuesday, the volcano in Iceland was still erupting, though the cloud was lower.
sentences.chinese: 截至周二，冰岛火山仍在喷发，但火山灰云有所降低。

sentences.english: For another, there are also some differences between high school life and college school.
sentences.chinese: 另一方面，高中生活和大学又有所不同。

sentences.english: Thorpe also showed that the chaffinch is selective imitate.
sentences.chinese: 索普还证明，苍头燕雀学歌是有所选择的。

sentences.english: Actually, it is one of the few industries that does.
sentences.chinese: 实际上，这里有所回报的行业屈指可数。

sentences.english: Menon however refrained from blaming Pakistan for the blasts.
sentences.chinese: 梅农对爆炸的指责有所控制，没有直接指向巴基斯坦。

sentences.english: When you have a realization, write it down in your journal.
sentences.chinese: 当你有所领悟时，把它们记在你的日记里。

sentences.english: Something that helped me get a handle on this was mini tasking my to-do list.
sentences.chinese: 有所帮助的事就是将要做的清单上的任务再细分。

sentences.english: However, times may vary since this training is self-paced.
sentences.chinese: 然而，时间可能有所不同，因为这次培训是自定进度。

sentences.english: Cells in different parts of the endosperm vary somewhat in composition.
sentences.chinese: 细胞在胚乳的不同部分其组成有所不同。

sentences.english: Those who haven't prepared themselves to be creative rarely are.
sentences.chinese: 而那些没有准备好做什么的人很难有所创造。
